creator: Doers Technology
descriptionHtml:
Satellite view & GPS navigation is new feature with the help of which user can easily commute from one location to another. This satellite map application with awesome features. Lets its user to be on right place and at right time with its satellite view earth map of traffic around. En-route where you want to be and get live location update of driving directions.

This satellite map live earth assists as route finder if you are new to certain place. You can simply enter the address to find live location just in seconds. Satellite map with navigation will guide you turn by turn heading towards your destination. There are different satellite map styles like hybrid, terrain and gps location that further ease the usability of app.This GPS navigation will act as guide of your tour and you will not face any difficulty in satellite map while touring.

GPS Navigation Earth Map:
This satellite view is more useful when you want to go anywhere but you do not know exact directions. You can find with current location along with the place where you want to be. The route map would be shown; you can start navigation with the help of GPS location. Turn by turn GPS navigation will guide your way for easy and convenient journey.

Live Satellite View & GPS Location:
You will find different kind of map views are there in this application but the best one to look out for is the satellite view, which is real-time. This live satellite view enables users to seen 3d map of places. This feature proves to be very helpful for users in order to plan their route with help of gps navigation.

Voice Navigation Earth Map:
You must have experienced, nowadays people do not like typing on cellphone keyboard instead, they prefer voice note approach. This Gps location enables the voice map navigation with best voice recognition system. Tap on mic icon and speak the location, which you want to be at. The map will be displayed in few seconds after your voice map navigation instructions.

Famous Places:
You can find important places near in this satellite map. You can easily reach all the wonders of world, their route plan, their live satellite map and much more in seconds. Navigate towards your favorite famous location with single tap in gps navigation.

Save Routes:
This gps location with satellite live map enables user to make all the important routes saved. Navigate anywhere and save the route with ease. Tap on save route button and save your route plan. the saved route is in storage and can be handful in future for travelling purpose.

Area Measurement:
Find all the coordinates with proper accuracy in area measurement feature. Pin on points around which you want to measure the area. The best area measurement via GPS location will calculate area in inches , feet and cms.

Find Compass:
In this satellite view you will enable user to find right direction at right time. Just tap on compass and head towards the directions you want to. The best template of compass will enable user to use it with accuracy.

Speedometer:
This satellite map will provide you to find precise speed of your vehicle or your run within seconds. This awesome feature will avoid you to over speeding with gps speedometer app.

ISD/STD Code:
Now it’s easy to find ISD/STD codes of any country or any city in just one click. Find your codes with this prestigious app.

This GPS location app if you don’t want to get late to reach your office, any event etc. The real time satellite map is here to guide you all the way until your destination. The Traffic info will indicate at which point of your route there is traffic jam, or slightly slow traffic.
